definitions.title: n.pr.m.
definitions.body: (Who is what God is ? Ass. form., cf. [[מְתוּשָׁאֵל]]: note also in Thothmes’ list of towns Bai-ti-š-’-ra,i.e prob. [[בֵּיתְשָׁאֵל]], Heb. [[בֵּיתְאֵל]] WMM:As. Eur.193):—
a cousin of Moses Ex 6:22, Le 10:4 (P).
one of Daniel's companions Da 1:5, Da 1:7, Da 1:11, Da 1:19 + Da 2:17 (Aram.), elsewhere in c. Da 2–Da 3 called [[מֵישַׁח]] (Da 1:7).
